@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam defaultFontName SansSerif
skinparam defaultFontSize 13
skinparam ArrowColor #333333
skinparam ActivityBackgroundColor #F5F5F5
skinparam ActivityBorderColor #666666

title Histogram Equalization — Three-Stage Algorithm

|Stage 1 — Build Histogram|
start
:Input image\n(packed int[], W×H);
fork
  :Thread 1 computes\npartial histogram\nfor columns [0, C₁);
fork again
  :Thread 2 computes\npartial histogram\nfor columns [C₁, C₂);
fork again
  :Thread N computes\npartial histogram\nfor columns [Cₙ₋₁, W);
end fork
:Main thread merges\nN partial histograms\n→ 256-bin global histogram;

|Stage 2 — Cumulative Prefix Sum|
:Sequential prefix sum\nover 256 bins\n(≈ 256 additions);

|Stage 3 — Equalization|
fork
  :Thread 1 applies\nequalization mapping\nto columns [0, C₁);
fork again
  :Thread 2 applies\nequalization mapping\nto columns [C₁, C₂);
fork again
  :Thread N applies\nequalization mapping\nto columns [Cₙ₋₁, W);
end fork
:Output image\n(packed int[], W×H);

stop
@enduml
